Title: Object: The flight into Egypt
Series: Houghton Gallery
Description: Mary sits on an ass, holding the Christ child in her arms; Joseph walks beside her, above them fly three putti; published state. 1778 Mezzotint
Curator's comments: From 'The Houghton Gallery', see 2005,U.109 for comment. Printed on the same sheet as 1917,1208.2479.
